<article class="indiv-product">

  <script type="application/json" id="product-grid-7459659186325" class="product-grid-json">
    {"id":7459659186325,"title":"May Box: Brighten","handle":"may-box-brighten","description":"\u003cp\u003eAs the days grow longer and brighter, we need to prep and protect for the coming summer fun! This box features an illuminating and protective moisturizer, a pit scrub that brightens and deodorizes, a richly restorative hair mask, an acne-fighting exfoliating sponge, and a lovely lavender sanitizer.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cstrong\u003eAble Skincare: 2-1 Glycolic Blue Light Exfoliating \u0026amp; Illuminating DUO Moisturizer ($107 Value)\u003c\/strong\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe all know how damaging sunlight can be—but did you know another culprit of premature aging is lurking inside your home? That’s right: blue light, from your beloved digital devices, causes damage to skin, too! But fear not. Our highest-value product to ever be featured in a box, this illuminating two-in-one moisturizer will keep your skin hydrated, exfoliated, and protected against blue light and other pollutants.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cstrong\u003eMudmasky: Saved by the Scrub for Underarms ($29 Value\u003c\/strong\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTank tops and swimsuits are coming—so now’s the time to get your pits in tip-top shape! This balancing scrub does it all for the sensitive, oft-neglected area under your arms: removes dead skin cells using premium kaolin clay; stimulates cell turnover to lighten skin; and reduces those annoying red bumps that can come after harsh cleansing. And forget masking BO—this scrub eliminates it entirely using upcycled coffee grounds to deeply cleanse and neutralize odor.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cstrong\u003eLoba Mane: Transformative Hair Mask ($12 Value)\u003c\/strong\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDid you know your hair can suffer from sun damage, too? As those rays get stronger, give your hair the protection it deserves with this sweet-smelling mask. Tucuma protects strands from UV rays, buriti strengthens, and coconut adds radiance. This mask prolongs hair color and restores an enviable moisturized sheen even after chemical treatments and too much styling. So mask up!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cstrong\u003eJ\u0026amp;L Naturals: Konjac Sponge Green Tea ($7.99 Value)\u003c\/strong\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMeet nature’s best exfoliant. Made from natural, biodegradable konjac root, this tiny but mighty tool is extremely gentle as it sloughs away dead skin to reveal a radiant glow. Infused with green tea for added antioxidants and anti-inflammatory benefits, this sponge is perfect for acne-prone skin and will leave nothing behind to dull your shine.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cstrong\u003eAll Good: Lavender Hand Sanitizer Spray ($4 Value)\u003c\/strong\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt’s always a good idea to remain vigilant against pesky pathogens. That’s why this fast-evaporating spray will be the first line of defense for your hands. Using only non-irritating ingredients, this all-natural spray kills germs, moisturizes skin, and leaves you with a soothing lavender scent.\u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2022-07-01T14:28:43-06:00","created_at":"2022-04-18T10:08:40-06:00","vendor":"Kinder Beauty","type":"","tags":["exclude_rebuy"],"price":2600,"price_min":2600,"price_max":2600,"available":false,"price_varies":false,"compare_at_price":15999,"compare_at_price_min":15999,"compare_at_price_max":15999,"compare_at_price_varies":false,"variants":[{"id":42203216478357,"title":"Default Title","option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":null,"available":false,"name":"May Box: Brighten","public_title":null,"options":["Default Title"],"price":2600,"weight":0,"compare_at_price":15999,"inventory_management":"shopify","barcode":"","requires_selling_plan":false,"selling_plan_allocations":[]}],"images":["\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_Brighten_Box_CYB_1000x1000_5efae498-0f49-4966-b170-aa7f3cb34347.jpg?v=1650299244","\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_Able_Skincare_Blue_Light_Exfoliating_1000x1000_dfb7fa4f-5b8a-41f5-a244-230bd6fcfebc.jpg?v=1650299145","\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_J_L_Naturals_Konjac_Sponge_box_1000x1000_caff272f-78ee-49dc-a889-f4eff0174c41.jpg?v=1650299145","\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_Pure_Scrub_for_Underarm_1000x1000_068a4eb4-3ea0-4952-9c7e-897d67c6cabe.jpg?v=1650299145","\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_Loba_Mane_Transformative_Mask_1000x1000_16871c6d-0f09-4088-ae9f-4a9c9e9e6d17.jpg?v=1650299145","\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_All_Good_Hand_Sanitizer_1000x1000_9288b07f-edbf-44cd-b294-64accb81e4b6.jpg?v=1650299145"],"featured_image":"\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_Brighten_Box_CYB_1000x1000_5efae498-0f49-4966-b170-aa7f3cb34347.jpg?v=1650299244","options":["Title"],"media":[{"alt":null,"id":26545978376341,"position":1,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1000,"width":1000,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_Brighten_Box_CYB_1000x1000_5efae498-0f49-4966-b170-aa7f3cb34347.jpg?v=1650299244"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1000,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_Brighten_Box_CYB_1000x1000_5efae498-0f49-4966-b170-aa7f3cb34347.jpg?v=1650299244","width":1000},{"alt":null,"id":26545935909013,"position":2,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1000,"width":1000,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_Able_Skincare_Blue_Light_Exfoliating_1000x1000_dfb7fa4f-5b8a-41f5-a244-230bd6fcfebc.jpg?v=1650299145"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1000,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_Able_Skincare_Blue_Light_Exfoliating_1000x1000_dfb7fa4f-5b8a-41f5-a244-230bd6fcfebc.jpg?v=1650299145","width":1000},{"alt":null,"id":26545933648021,"position":3,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1000,"width":1000,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_J_L_Naturals_Konjac_Sponge_box_1000x1000_caff272f-78ee-49dc-a889-f4eff0174c41.jpg?v=1650299145"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1000,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_J_L_Naturals_Konjac_Sponge_box_1000x1000_caff272f-78ee-49dc-a889-f4eff0174c41.jpg?v=1650299145","width":1000},{"alt":null,"id":26545935581333,"position":4,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1000,"width":1000,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_Pure_Scrub_for_Underarm_1000x1000_068a4eb4-3ea0-4952-9c7e-897d67c6cabe.jpg?v=1650299145"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1000,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_Pure_Scrub_for_Underarm_1000x1000_068a4eb4-3ea0-4952-9c7e-897d67c6cabe.jpg?v=1650299145","width":1000},{"alt":null,"id":26545934532757,"position":5,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1000,"width":1000,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_Loba_Mane_Transformative_Mask_1000x1000_16871c6d-0f09-4088-ae9f-4a9c9e9e6d17.jpg?v=1650299145"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1000,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_Loba_Mane_Transformative_Mask_1000x1000_16871c6d-0f09-4088-ae9f-4a9c9e9e6d17.jpg?v=1650299145","width":1000},{"alt":null,"id":26545934762133,"position":6,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1000,"width":1000,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_All_Good_Hand_Sanitizer_1000x1000_9288b07f-edbf-44cd-b294-64accb81e4b6.jpg?v=1650299145"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1000,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220831113339\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/KB_Website_All_Good_Hand_Sanitizer_1000x1000_9288b07f-edbf-44cd-b294-64accb81e4b6.jpg?v=1650299145","width":1000}],"requires_selling_plan":false,"selling_plan_groups":[],"content":"\u003cp\u003eAs the days grow longer and brighter, we need to prep and protect for the coming summer fun! This box features an illuminating and protective moisturizer, a pit scrub that brightens and deodorizes, a richly restorative hair mask, an acne-fighting exfoliating sponge, and a lovely lavender sanitizer.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cstrong\u003eAble Skincare: 2-1 Glycolic Blue Light Exfoliating \u0026amp; Illuminating DUO Moisturizer ($107 Value)\u003c\/strong\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe all know how damaging sunlight can be—but did you know another culprit of premature aging is lurking inside your home? That’s right: blue light, from your beloved digital devices, causes damage to skin, too! But fear not. Our highest-value product to ever be featured in a box, this illuminating two-in-one moisturizer will keep your skin