                  <div class="feature-row__text--inner">
                    
                        
													<h2 class="underline--brush"><span class="wow fadeIn">Behind the</span> <span class="wow fadeIn delay-1 header--script header__highlight">beauty box</span></h2>
                        
                    
                    
                      <div class="rte featured-row__subtext textarea"><p>Kinder Beauty Box was co-founded by actresses and ethical entrepreneurs, Daniella Monet and Evanna Lynch. Daniella and Evy are both long-time animal activists and self-care enthusiasts, with a deep passion for curating the very best ethical beauty products on the market.</p></div>
                    
                    
                      <a href="/web/20220831113339/https://kinderbeauty.com/pages/our-founders-daniella-monet-and-evanna-lynch" class="btn btn-outline">
                        Meet Our Founders
                      </a>
                    
                  </div>
